2
00:01:08,410 --> 00:01:11,650
我只是想走前最后看你一眼
I just wanted to see you one last time before I leave.

3
00:01:11,660 --> 00:01:13,470
我觉得没什么好说的了
I don't believe there's anything left to be said.

4
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:16,240
我俩确实无话可说了
No, not between us. Not any longer.

5
00:01:16,390 --> 00:01:19,090
我只是想谢谢
I just wanted to thank you for...

6
00:01:19,970 --> 00:01:22,000
你的韧劲
your tenacity.

7
00:01:24,290 --> 00:01:26,220
无论你想干什么  你都无法逍遥法外
Whatever you're up to, you won't get away with it.

8
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,280
也许我已经做到了
Maybe I already have.

9
00:01:28,810 --> 00:01:30,560
委员会将继续工作
The committee will continue its work.

10
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,600
我们会建议司法部提出起诉
We'll recommend charges to DOJ.

11
00:01:33,450 --> 00:01:34,810
罗谢尔
Rochelle.

12
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:47,560
罗谢尔
Rochelle.

13
00:01:49,010 --> 00:01:51,010
多美的名字
Such a lovely name.

14
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:55,890
告诉我你有多么不想那名字上新闻
Tell me how much you don't want that to end up in the press.

15
00:01:56,780 --> 00:01:59,430
然后解散这个委员会
And then shut this committee down.

16
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,650
你得无条件听我的
No deals.

