548
00:37:35,790 --> 00:37:37,780
你会像个绅士一样走出去
You will walk out of here like a gentleman.

549
00:37:37,780 --> 00:37:40,780
我们要他12小时内面见法官
We want him in front of the judge within 12 hours.

550
00:37:40,780 --> 00:37:43,290
我们还不知道是否会起诉他
We don't even know if we're gonna charge him yet.

551
00:37:43,290 --> 00:37:44,600
是我做的
I did it.

552
