我有些建议  已经传达给马克了
I have some suggestions I've passed on to Mark.

580
00:39:04,450 --> 00:39:07,890
我认为中情局的副局长  玛茜·西格森
I think Deputy Director of the CIA, Marcy Siegerson,

581
