602
00:40:19,020 --> 00:40:22,750
任何能把你和选举联系起来的有力证据...
Any hard evidence connecting you to the election...

603
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:24,610
都在她手上
is in her hands.

604
00:40:25,020 --> 00:40:27,100
那么莉安的工作结束了
Then LeAnn's job is done.

605
00:41:14,830 --> 00:41:17,820
如果你还有什么要说的  现在是时候了
If you have anything to say, now is the time.

606
00:41:21,690 --> 00:41:23,340
你觉得发生了什么
What do you think happened?

607
00:41:25,530 --> 00:41:27,330
我更希望你来告诉我
I'd prefer you tell me that.

608
00:41:27,330 --> 00:41:30,470
迁就我吧  是你要求见面的
Humor me. You asked for this meeting.

609
00:41:31,430 --> 00:41:33,010
你觉得发生了什么
What do you think happened?

610
00:41:38,120 --> 00:41:40,020
我相信佐伊·巴恩斯当时在调查
I believe Zoe Barnes was investigating

