620
00:42:13,350 --> 00:42:16,010
我不知道瑞秋·波斯纳怎么了
I don't know what happened to Rachel Posner.

621
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:19,140
但是我不相信是你杀了佐伊·巴恩斯
But I don't believe you killed Zoe Barnes.

622
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:23,190
录像里的是你吗
Is this you in this video?

623
00:42:28,620 --> 00:42:29,880
看起来像是我
Looks like me.

624
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:46,490
我仔细思考了很久  弗兰西斯
I've thought long and hard, Francis.

625
00:42:47,250 --> 00:42:48,720
几乎没睡
Barely slept.

626
