644
00:43:59,770 --> 00:44:02,170
将全面无条件地赦免
A full and unconditional pardon...

645
00:44:03,080 --> 00:44:06,020
弗兰西斯·安德伍德在担任美国总统期间
for Francis Underwood and any crimes he might have committed

646
00:44:06,020 --> 00:44:08,620
可能犯下的任何罪行
against the United States while president.

647
00:44:10,120 --> 00:44:11,600
