I'm glad to hear that.

648
00:44:12,340 --> 00:44:16,650
我从没动摇过  我只是需要考虑一下方式
It was never in doubt. I just needed to think about how.

649
00:44:19,590 --> 00:44:22,060
那这个安排要维持多久
So how long does this arrangement last?

650
00:44:22,570 --> 00:44:24,020
暂时先这样吧
For the time being.

651
00:44:26,840 --> 00:44:29,470
我们是怎么到这一步的  弗兰西斯
How did we get here, Francis?

652
00:44:29,960 --> 00:44:31,630
别纠结了  已经过去了
Oh, let it go. It's done.

653
