这个人就是你真正应该小心的人
that's the person that you're really gonna have to watch.

656
00:44:43,510 --> 00:44:46,080
我应付不了的人  我是不会选的
I won't choose anyone I can't manage.

657
00:45:31,140 --> 00:45:33,200
在楼的西南角  继续观察
Southwest corner of the building. Maintain visual.

658
00:45:33,200 --> 00:45:34,450
收到
Copy that.

659
00:45:35,100 --> 00:45:36,370
扔雷
Frag out!

660
00:45:38,850 --> 00:45:41,050
艾哈迈迪在那儿  我看到艾哈迈迪了
There's Ahmadi. I have visual on Ahmadi.

661
00:45:41,090 --> 00:45:43,450
-我看到他了  -冲  开火
- I see him. - Go, go! Fire!

662
00:45:49,730 --> 00:45:51,690
我犯了个大错
I made a terrible mistake.

663
00:45:54,820 --> 00:45:56,120
你做了什么
What did you do?

664
00:45:57,510 --> 00:45:59,800
我都不知道我在做什么  我
I don't even know what I'm doing here. I, uh...

665
00:46:01,050 --> 00:46:04,370
早上我开着车就出来了  我怕了
This morning I started driving. I... I got scared.

666
00:46:06,630 --> 00:46:08,980
总之我正往回赶  我能去见你吗
Anyway, I'm on my way back. Can I come see you?

667
00:46:09,640 --> 00:46:10,910
当然
Yes, please.

668
00:46:16,300 --> 00:46:18,220
{\pos(164.1,63)}道格·斯坦普

