00:48:28,190 --> 00:48:29,970
艾哈迈德·艾哈迈迪
Ahmed Al Ahmadi.

700
00:48:30,270 --> 00:48:31,650
我们干掉他了
We got him.

701
00:48:32,700 --> 00:48:33,970
我们消灭他了
We got him.

702
00:48:34,960 --> 00:48:37,890
在每一位男女总统任职期间
Now, there comes a time in every president's tenure

703
00:48:37,900 --> 00:48:41,830
他们总会面临这么一个问题  就是要不要
when he or she must face the question of whether or not

704
00:48:41,960 --> 00:48:45,370
派遣美国年轻人上阵杀敌
to send young American soldiers into harm's way.

705
00:48:46,100 --> 00:48:47,610
对我而言
In my case...

706
00:48:47,990 --> 00:48:52,660
我上任之初  就要面对这个难题了
that time has fallen within the very first days of my presidency.

707
00:48:53,550 --> 00:48:57,470
俄罗斯总统维克多·佩特罗夫与中国合谋
Russian President Viktor Petrov collaborated with the Chinese

708
00:48:57,470 --> 00:49:00,830
试图在南极洲非法开采石油
on illegal oil exploration in Antarctica.

709
00:49:00,830 --> 00:49:04,040
最近我们又了解到  他已派出军队
Recently, we have learned that he has sent troops

710
00:49:04,040 --> 00:49:06,350
与叙利亚当局并肩作战
to fight alongside the Syrian regime,

711
00:49:06,350 --> 00:49:09,730
协助他们毁灭叙利亚国家
assisting them in the destruction of the Syrian nation.

712
00:49:09,910 --> 00:49:13,630
政府军使用化学武器攻击自己的人民
These forces are using chemical weapons on their own people,

713
00:49:13,640 --> 00:49:15,350
折磨异议人士
torturing the opposition,

714
00:49:15,350 --> 00:49:18,270
让全国绝大多数人口忍饥挨饿
and starving huge segments of the population.

715
00:49:18,370 --> 00:49:20,820
叙利亚人民已饱受战乱之苦
The Syrians are a people besieged.

716
00:49:21,110 --> 00:49:24,240
不要再让他们被遗忘了
Let them not also be forgotten.

717
00:49:24,330 --> 00:49:28,540
我们将怒火转化成行动的时机已经到来
The time has come for our outrage to be turned into action.

718
00:49:29,540 --> 00:49:30,900
五个月前  我丈夫
Five months ago, my husband

719
00:49:30,900 --> 00:49:33,230
曾向众议院发出呼吁
addressed the House of Representatives

720
00:49:33,230 --> 00:49:36,370
要求他们向哈里发国宣战
and asked them to declare war on ICO.

721
00:49:36,820 --> 00:49:38,530
国会让他失望了
Congress failed him.

722
00:49:39,460 --> 00:49:41,580
国会让人民失望了
Congress failed you.

723
00:49:42,240 --> 00:49:46,590
哈里发国极端分子图谋让我们的民主和国家
ICO extremists want democracy and America itself

724
00:49:46,590 --> 00:49:48,800
轰然崩塌
to die a fiery death.

725
00:49:49,310 --> 00:49:51,710
我们决不能让他们得逞
We cannot allow that to happen.

726
00:49:51,980 --> 00:49:54,360
我们不能再等待国会了
We can't wait for Congress any longer.

727
00:49:54,370 --> 00:49:56,780
我们给国会的机会已经够多了
We gave Congress every chance.

728
00:49:57,210 --> 00:49:58,940
她是不打算说了
She isn't going to say it.

729
00:49:59,980 --> 00:50:03,150
历史在评判每一位领袖  每一位总统的时候
Now, history judges every leader, every president,

730
00:50:03,330 --> 00:50:06,860
都要看他或她是怎么对待自己的人民的
by how he or she treats his or her own people.

731
00:50:06,860 --> 00:50:11,710
一个悍然攻击医院  难民营
A regime that would target hospitals, refugee camps,

732
00:50:11,860 --> 00:50:13,570
学校和救济车队
schools or bread lines

733
00:50:13,570 --> 00:50:17,460
只为了自保的政权  必须受到惩罚
in order to retain power must be confronted.

734
00:50:17,460 --> 00:50:19,160
而身为国家领袖  却牺牲
A leader that would sacrifice

735
00:50:19,160 --> 00:50:22,890
自己人民的幸福安康
the physical and emotional well-being of his citizens,

736
00:50:23,490 --> 00:50:26,020
视人民如棋子筹码
that would treat his people as pawns,

737
00:50:26,020 --> 00:50:28,890
就为了保住自己的权力
just to stay in power? Well...

738
00:50:29,370 --> 00:50:32,170
这样的领袖必须下台
that leader needs to be stopped.

739
00:50:35,650 --> 00:50:37,690
如果她不赦免我
If she doesn't pardon me...

740
00:50:39,030 --> 00:50:40,480
我就杀了她
I'll kill her.

741
00:50:42,050 --> 00:50:45,420
谢谢你们  上帝保佑我们伟大的国家
Thank you and God bless this great country.

742
00:50:53,040 --> 00:50:55,360
电话已经涌进来了
Well, the calls are coming in already.

743
00:50:55,390 --> 00:50:57,230
讲得好  今晚对你非常有利
Well done. This'll be a good night for you.

744
00:50:57,490 --> 00:50:58,450
莫斯科那边还没有动静
Nothing from Moscow yet.

745
00:50:58,450 --> 00:51:00,660
现在我想自己待一会儿
Right now I just need some time to myself.

746
00:51:06,540 --> 00:51:08,090
你认识汤姆·耶茨吗
Do you know Tom Yates?

747
00:51:08,470 --> 00:51:09,730
不熟  怎么了
Not personally. Why?

748
00:51:10,120 --> 00:51:12,060
他有段时间没出现了
He hasn't been around in a while.

749
00:51:13,010 --> 00:51:14,470
没事  算了
I don't know, forget it.

750
00:51:15,480 --> 00:51:16,600
怎么了
What?

751
00:51:16,990 --> 00:51:20,370
我一直在联系他  而他通常都回电话的
I've been calling him. And he usually answers.

752
00:51:21,560 --> 00:51:24,170
我们要正义  我们要和平
We demand justice, we demand peace!

753
