中东不要再打仗
No more war in the Middle East!

754
00:51:26,650 --> 00:51:29,190
我们要正义  我们要和平
We demand justice, we demand peace!

755
00:51:29,190 --> 00:51:31,620
中东不要再打仗
No more war in the Middle East!

756
00:51:31,620 --> 00:51:34,160
我们要正义  我们要和平
We demand justice, we demand peace!

757
00:51:34,160 --> 00:51:36,670
中东不要再打仗
No more war in the Middle East!

758
00:51:36,670 --> 00:51:39,210
我们要正义  我们要和平
We demand justice, we demand peace...

759
00:51:39,830 --> 00:51:42,210
{\an7}{\pos(123,193.95)}抗议者在白宫草坪被击毙

760
00:51:39,950 --> 00:51:42,250
白宫外爆发的反战示威游行
The anti- war demonstrations outside the White House

761
00:51:42,250 --> 00:51:43,070
终于出了状况
finally got out of hand.

762
00:51:43,070 --> 00:51:45,910
这里是莉安·哈维  请留言
You've reached LeAnn Harvey. Please leave a message.

763
00:51:46,180 --> 00:51:48,660
一名抗议者翻过围栏
One of the protesters made his way over the gates.

764
00:51:48,660 --> 00:51:50,560
在穿越白宫草坪的时候
As he was running across the White House lawn,

765
00:51:50,570 --> 00:51:52,470
被赶来的特勤局特工包围
Secret Service agents moved in,

766
00:51:52,480 --> 00:51:54,770
该名抗议者不幸被击毙
tragically shooting and killing the man.

767
00:52:02,850 --> 00:52:05,600
这里是莉安·哈维  请留言
You've reached LeAnn Harvey. Please leave a message.

768
00:52:05,600 --> 00:52:07,410
你在哪呢
Hey, where are you?

769
00:52:41,650 --> 00:52:43,950
抱歉  女士  今晚是不行了
I'm sorry, ma'am, it's just not possible tonight.

770
00:52:44,340 --> 00:52:45,530
我们无法确保跑步路线安全
We can't secure the run.

771
00:52:45,530 --> 00:52:47,880
目前威胁等级太高了
The level of threat at this point is just too high.

772
00:52:48,910 --> 00:52:51,000
-好的  谢谢你  -好的  女士
- Okay. Thank you. - Yes, ma'am.

